Privacy Policy
Introduction
Welcome to Tic Tac Toe! We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our app.

By using the app, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

Information We Collect
Third-Party Services
We may integrate third-party services, such as advertising networks (e.g., Huawei Ads), analytics tools, or storage services, that collect information about your interactions within the app.

How We Use Your Information
We may use the information collected for the following purposes:

To provide and maintain the app's functionality.
To personalize your experience.
To improve and enhance app performance.
To display relevant ads.
To comply with legal obligations or resolve disputes.
Third-Party Services and Advertising
We use third-party services like Huawei Ads and others to display advertisements. These services may collect information, such as:

Device identifiers.
Interaction data with ads.
Please review the privacy policies of these third-party services for more details.

Data Sharing and Security
1. Data Sharing
We do not sell or rent your personal data to third parties. However, we may share your data with:

Trusted third-party service providers who assist in operating the app.
Legal entities, if required by law or to protect our rights.
2. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, no method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

Your Rights
Depending on your location, you may have the following rights:

The right to access and correct your data.
The right to request the deletion of your data.
The right to opt-out of personalized advertising.
To exercise these rights, please contact us at gkyando5@gmail.com.

